Quiz 1) Learn Tile names - Multiple choice quiz that never ends\
In Quiz 1, you are given 5 tiles and a question to identify a tile by its name. Although tiles can be named by the number of dots they have you should also know their names to make it easy to play. (you get 3 chances to guess before the answer is revealed)\
