Quiz 2) Learn Pair ranks - Multiple choice quiz that never ends \
This quiz builds on your Quiz 1 skills and lets you pick tiles of a particular "Rank" from 5 randomly drawn tiles. This rank is the pair ranking for any given tile. Play this game to familiarize with the ranks of the tile in case you get a pair. (you get 3 chances to guess before the answer is revealed)\
\
Quiz 3) Compare tile ranks (to pick the higher tile) - Another quiz that never ends\
You are given 2 random tiles and you have to tap the tile which has the higher rank. (from the pair ranks)\
\
Quiz 4) [available in Paigow Tutor Pro]  Compare 2 paigow hands\
You are given 2 sets of Paigow Hands. You will have to pick the higher values hand. (in case of a tie, both answers will be correct)\
